data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY, 12/10 from 12:30-2:00pm!!! Located less than two miles from the renown Riverwatch Golf Club, this home is everything you've been looking for! Situated on 5.02 acres, this unrestricted property offers cleared, flat to rolling land surrounded by mature trees, and a large pond perfect for fishing and watering your animals! This property offers a brand new 30'x50' metal building, complete with 200 amp service and a 16'x50' lean-to. Inside you'll find 1,404 finished sqft on the main level with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and tons of updates! Downstairs you'll find a finished basement with 2 additional bedrooms, multiple living spaces, and another full bathroom. Schedule your showing today!!
